Features Summary

1. ✅ Auto Reply DMs - Toggle with .autoreply on/off
2. ✅ Auto Reply Groups - Toggle with .autoreplygrp on/off
3. ✅ Chatbot - Separate from auto reply, toggle with .chatbot on/off
4. ✅ Auto View Status - Automatically views status updates
5. ✅ Auto Like Status - Automatically likes status updates
6. ✅ Auto Typing - Shows typing indicator in DMs
7. ✅ Auto Recording - Shows recording indicator in DMs
8. ✅ Anti Delete - Forwards deleted messages to owner
9. ✅ Anti Link - Removes links and warns users
10. ✅ Auto Follow Channel - Automatically follows your channel
11. ✅ Auto Join Group - Automatically joins your group
12. ✅ View Once - Command to view view-once messages
13. ✅ Button Menus - All commands use interactive buttons
14. ✅ Font Styling - All messages use the special fonts you requested

Commands Available

· .menu - Main menu with buttons
· .allmenu - Show all commands
· .features - Show features status
· .owner - Owner information
· .ping - Check bot speed
· .alive - Check if bot is online
· .repo - Get GitHub repository
· .song [name/url] - Download songs
· .viewonce - View view-once messages (owner only)

Feature Control Commands (Owner Only)

· .autoreply on/off - Toggle DM auto reply
· .autoreplygrp on/off - Toggle group auto reply
· .chatbot on/off - Toggle chatbot
· .autoview on/off - Toggle auto view status
· .autolike on/off - Toggle auto like status
· .antidelete on/off - Toggle anti delete
· .antilink on/off - Toggle anti link

Bot itaanza na features zote ON kama ulivyoomba. Unaweza kuzizima kwa kutumia commands hizo za owner.
